\section{Video Making for Conferences or YouTube}

\begin{itemize}
\item Rehearse talk 10 times at least to reduce time consuming editing latter on.
\item Remove background from webcam image see \url{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9iEjxM2SF6o}
\item Record talk with OBS or in Zoom.
\item Convert video to mp4 in OBS
\item Edit video in Blender.
\item Transsfer video via secure file transfer.
\end{itemize}
